_header: Blessed Gabriel which broughtest first tiding
Subjects: prayers, to guardian angel; Gabriel, archangel
_description: A prayer to Gabriel (by Lydgate?) — one 8-line stanza

BodLauMis683.First Lines:
Blissed Gabriel wich broughtest first tydyngon to marye knelyng on
                    thy kne…
BodLauMis683.Last Lines:
…for wich o Gabriel geyn all aduersytebe thow our helpe whan
                    we to the calle

MacCracken,  Henry Noble,
